bject-page"><a href="https://www.federaltitle.com/dc-homestead-deduction/"> Homestead Deduction /</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.federaltitle.com/dc-first-time-homebuyer-reduced-tax/"> Reduced Recordation /</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-post"><a href="https://www.federaltitle.com/dc-first-time-home-buyer/"> First-Time Homebuyer</a></li></ul></div></div></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom uk-parent"><a href="https://closeit.federaltitle.com" target="_blank" class="uk-preserve-width"><span class="uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="icon: phone;"></span> Close It!</a><div class="uk-navbar-dropdown" style="width: 400px;"><div class="uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-child-width-1-1 uk-grid-margin"><div class="uk-width-1-1"></div></div></div></li></ul></div></nav></div></div></div></header><main id="tm-main" ><div class="uk-section-default uk-light uk-position-relative"><div style="background-size: 250px 250px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" data-src="/wp-content/themes/yootheme/cache/1a/Emely-Toro-Headshot-1a534ed2.jpeg" data-sources="[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image\/webp&quot;,&quot;srcset&quot;:&quot;\/wp-content\/themes\/yootheme\/cache\/0e\/Emely-Toro-Headshot-0e9857b7.webp 250w, \/wp-content\/themes\/yootheme\/cache\/2c\/Emely-Toro-Headshot-2cf44e16.webp 500w&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:&quot;(min-width: 250px) 250px&quot;}]" uk-img class="uk-background-norepeat uk-background-top-left uk-background-fixed uk-section"><div class="uk-position-cover" style="background-color: rgba(108, 101, 101, 0.8);"></div><div class="uk-position-relative"><div class="uk-position-relative uk-panel"><div class="uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-child-width-1-1 uk-grid-margin"><div class="uk-width-1-1@m"><div class="uk-panel uk-margin-remove-vertical uk-text-center"><p style="font-weight: 400;">Emely Toro is a settlement attorney with experience managing complex transactions and resolving title-related issues. She was born and raised in Orlando, Florida and received her juris doctor from Georgetown University Law Center.  Whether you&#8217;re buying, selling, or refinancing a property, Emely provides expert legal services to ensure that every transaction is completed smoothly and securely. With a keen eye for detail and a deep understanding of real estate law, she helps clients navigate the complexities of title searches, title insurance, and clearing title defects. Emely’s commitment to protecting her clients’ interests ensures that their closings are conducted with confidence and peace of mind.</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Outside of her legal career, Emely has a passion for real estate, particularly house flipping. She enjoys taking on renovation projects and transforming properties into beautiful homes, which gives her a unique, hands-on perspective when advising clients on property matters. Emely is an avid traveler and enjoys spending time outdoors, whether it’s hiking, biking, or enjoying a day at the beach.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="tm-section-title uk-position-top-left uk-position-medium uk-margin-remove-vertical uk-visible@xl"><div class="tm-rotate-180">Emely Toro</div></div></div></div></div><div class="uk-section-default uk-section uk-section-small"><div class="uk-container uk-container-xlarge"><div class="uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-child-width-1-1 uk-grid-margin"><div class="uk-width-1-1@m"><div class="uk-panel uk-text-lead uk-margin-small uk-margin-remove-bottom uk-width-2xlarge uk-margin-auto uk-text-center"><p>Search our website  or contact our <a href="/feedback" >webmaster</a>.</p><div class="uk-panel widget-search" id="widget-search-2"><form class="uk-search uk-search-default" id="search-713" role="search" action="https://www.federaltitle.com/" method="get">
